兩種民調方法來瞭解民意仍然有無法克服的困難為何？請列出兩點，並
深入說明。（25分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:33:19+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a9ae3dabb94b", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111090", "c": "317", "s": "0712", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "民意與公共關係學概論", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": "一", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "heelevel3", "civil_category": "新聞(選試英文)"}'::jsonb, NULL),
